org.mmbase.storage.search.legacy

Class DBConditionItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mmbase.storage.search.legacy.ParseItem
      • org.mmbase.storage.search.legacy.DBConditionItem

  • class DBConditionItem
extends ParseItem
    Class for conversion of boolean xpressions to their SQL equivalent. This class converts the following conditional operators encountered in the parameter passed to the constructor :
    '=='' or '=E' to '='
    '=N' to '<>'
    '=G' to '>'
    '=g' to '>='
    '=S' to '<'
    '=s' to '<='
    It also wraps string values with the SQL lower() function, and uses LIKE when wildcards are used in a stringvalue.
